## Vault Structure

```
{{VAULT_PATH}}/
├── raw/                    # Immutable sources (language-neutral)
├── wiki/
│   ├── en/                 # English atoms
│   └── es/                 # Spanish atoms (same filenames)
├── moc/
│   ├── en/                 # English Maps of Content
│   └── es/                 # Spanish Maps of Content
├── index/
│   ├── en/index.md         # Tier-0 compact EN nav (≤150 tokens)
│   └── es/index.md         # Tier-0 compact ES nav
├── queries/
│   ├── en/                 # Cached EN responses
│   └── es/                 # Cached ES responses
└── meta/                   # Shared: contradictions, backlinks, glossary
```

